Catalyst-Authentication-OAuth-ServiceProvider

This distribution enables OAuth server provider authentication within
the Catalyst::Plugin::Authentication framwork.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Catalyst::Authentication::Credential::OAuth::ServiceProvider

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Catalyst-Authentication-OAuth-ServiceProvider

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Catalyst-Authentication-OAuth-ServiceProvider

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Catalyst-Authentication-OAuth-ServiceProvider

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Catalyst-Authentication-OAuth-ServiceProvider/


